tafc.com/matches/first-team/ |title=First Team 2019/20 |publisher=Huddersfield Town A.F.C. |accessdate=31 January 2020|df=dmy-all }}</ref>}}<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.htafc.com/matches/first-team/|title=First Team|publisher=Huddersfield Town A.F.C.|accessdate=3 August 2019}}</ref>\n\n{{fs start}}\n{{fs player|no=1  |nat=POL |pos=GK |name=[[Kamil Grabara]]|other=on loan from [[Liverpool F.C.|Liverpool]]}}\n{{fs player|no=3  |nat=ENG |pos=DF |name=[[Harry Toffolo]]|other=}}\n{{fs player|no=4  |nat=ENG |pos=DF |name=[[Tommy Elphick]]|other=}}\n{{fs player|no=6  |nat=ENG |pos=MF |name=[[Jonathan Hogg]]|other=}}\n{{fs player|no=7  |nat=CUR |pos=MF |name=[[Juninho Bacuna]]|other=}}\n{{fs player|no=8  |nat=ENG |pos=MF |name=[[Trevoh Chalobah]]|other=on loan from [[Chelsea F.C.|Chelsea]]}}\n{{fs player|no=9  |nat=DRC |pos=FW |name=[[Elias Kachunga]]|other=}}\n{{fs player|no=10 |nat=ENG |pos=MF |name=[[Chris Willock]]|other=on loan from [[S.L. Benfica|Benfica]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=12 |nat=ENG |pos=DF |name=[[Richard Stearman]]|other=}}\n{{Fs player|no=13 |nat=ENG |pos=GK |name=[[Joel Coleman]]|other=}}\n{{fs player|no=14 |nat=UGA |pos=DF |name=[[Herbert Bockhorn]]|other=}}\n{{fs player|no=16 |nat=ENG |pos=FW |name=[[Karlan Grant]]|other=}}\n{{fs player|no=17 |nat=ENG |pos=DF |name=[[Danny Simpson]]|other=}}\n{{fs mid}}\n{{fs player|no=21 |nat=ENG |pos=MF |name=[[Alex Pritchard]]|other=}}\n{{fs player|no=22 |nat=ENG |pos=FW |name=[[Fraizer Campbell]]|other=}}\n{{fs player|no=23 |nat=GER |pos=FW |name=[[Collin Quaner]]|other=}}\n{{fs player|no=24 |nat=BEN |pos=FW |name=[[Steve Mouni\u00e9]]|other=}}\n{{fs player|no=25 |nat=ENG |pos=FW |name=[[Rekeil Pyke]]|other=}}\n{{fs player|no=26 |nat=GER |pos=DF |name=[[Christopher Schindler]]|other=[[Captain (association football)|Captain]]}}\n{{fs player|no=27 |nat=SLO |pos=DF |name=[[Jon Gorenc Stankovi\u0107]]|other=}}\n{{fs player|no=28 |nat=ENG |pos=DF |name=[[Jaden Brown]]|other=}}\n{{fs player|no=29 |nat=WAL |pos=MF |name=[[Andy King (footballer, born 1988)|Andy King]]|other=on loan from [[Leicester City F.C.|Leicester City]]}}\n{{fs player|no=32 |nat=ENG |pos=MF |name=[[Emile Smith Rowe]]|other=on loan from [[Arsenal F.C.|Arsenal]]}}\n{{fs player|no=39 |nat=ENG |pos=MF |name=[[Lewis O'Brien (footballer)|Lewis O'Brien]]|other=}}\n{{fs player|no=41 |nat=ENG |pos=MF |name=[[Matty Daly]]|other=}}\n{{fs player|no=49 |nat=DEN |pos=GK |name=[[Jonas L\u00f6ssl]]|other=on loan from [[Everton F.C.|Everton]]}}\n{{fs end}}\n\n===Out on loan===\n{{fs start}}\n{{fs player|no=5  |nat=NED |pos=DF |name=[[Terence Kongolo]]|other=at [[Fulham F.C.|Fulham]] until 31 May 2020}}\n{{fs player|no=11 |nat=FRA |pos=MF |name=[[Adama Diakhaby]]|other=at [[Nottingham Forest F.C.|Nottingham Forest]] until 31 May 2020}}\n{{fs player|no=18 |nat=BEL |pos=MF |name=[[Isaac Mbenza]]|other=at [[Amiens SC]]}}\n{{fs player|no=19 |nat=ENG |pos=FW |name=[[Josh Koroma]]|other=at [[Rotherham United F.C.|Rotherham United]]}}\n{{fs player|no=20 |nat=ENG |pos=MF |name=[[Reece Brown (footballer, born 1996)|Reece Brown]]|other=at [[Peterborough United F.C.|Peterborough United]] until 31 May 2020}}\n{{fs mid}}\n{{fs player|no=31 |nat=ENG |pos=GK |name=[[Ryan Schofield]]|other=at [[Livingston F.C.|Livingston]] until 31 May 2020}}\n{{fs player|no=33 |nat=KOS |pos=DF |name=[[Florent Hadergjonaj]]|other=at [[Kas\u0131mpa\u015fa S.K.|Kas\u0131mpa\u015fa]] until 31 May 2020}}\n{{fs player|no=35 |nat=ENG |pos=DF |name=[[Rarmani Edmonds-Green]]|other=at [[Swindon Town F.C.|Swindon Town]] until 31 May 2020}}\n{{fs player|no=\u2014  |nat=ENG |pos=GK |name=[[Ben Hamer]]|other=at [[Derby County F.C.|Derby County]] until 31 May 2020}}\n{{fs player|no=\u2014  |nat=EGY |pos=MF |name=[[Ramadan Sobhi]]|other=at [[Al Ahly SC|Al Ahly]] until 31 May 2020}}\n{{fs end}}\n\n===Development squad===\n{{Main article|Huddersfield Town A.F.C. Reserves and Academy}}\n\n==Player achievements==\n===Full and U-21 Internationals===\nOnly players who gained caps while