ommy Smith]]\n*2015 \u2013 {{Flagicon|ENG}} [[Conor Coady]]\n*2016 \u2013 {{Flagicon|Denmark}} [[Philip Billing]]\n*2017 \u2013 {{Flagicon|Denmark}} [[Philip Billing]]\n*2018 \u2013 {{Flagicon|Kosovo}} [[Florent Hadergjonaj]]\n*2019 \u2013 {{Flagicon|Denmark}} [[Philip Billing]]\n\n==PFA Team of the Year==\n''The following have been included in the [[PFA Team of the Year]] whilst playing for Huddersfield Town:''\n* [[1975\u201376 in English football|1975\u201376]]: {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Geoff Hutt]] (Fourth Division)\n* [[1976\u201377 in English football|1976\u201377]]: {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Terry Poole (footballer, born 1949)|Terry Poole]] (Fourth Division)\n* [[1979\u201380 in English football|1979\u201380]]: {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Malcolm Brown (English footballer)|Malcolm Brown]], {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Ian Robins]] (Fourth Division)\n* [[1980\u201381 in English football|1980\u201381]]: {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Malcolm Brown (English footballer)|Malcolm Brown]] (Third Division)\n* [[1981\u201382 in English football|1981\u201382]]: {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Malcolm Brown (English footballer)|Malcolm Brown]] (Third Division)\n* [[1982\u201383 in English football|1982\u201383]]: {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Malcolm Brown (English footballer)|Malcolm Brown]] (Third Division)\n* [[1991\u201392 in English football|1991\u201392]]: {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Simon Charlton]], {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Chris Marsden]], {{flagicon|WAL}} [[Iwan Roberts]] (Third Division)\n* [[1992\u201393 in English football|1992\u201393]]: {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Simon Charlton]] (Division Two)\n* [[1994\u201395 in English football|1994\u201395]]: {{flagicon|SCO}} [[Tom Cowan]], {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Andy Booth]] (Division Two)\n* [[2003\u201304 in English football|2003\u201304]]: {{flagicon|NGR}} [[Efe Sodje]] (Division Three)\n* [[2010\u201311 in English football|2010\u201311]]: {{flagicon|IRL}} [[Anthony Pilkington]] (League One)\n* [[2011\u201312 in English football|2011\u201312]]: {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Jack Hunt (footballer)|Jack Hunt]], {{flagicon|SCO}} [[Jordan Rhodes]] (League One)\n* [[2016\u201317 in English football|2016\u201317]]: {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Aaron Mooy]] (Championship)\n\n==League history==\n{{Main article|List of Huddersfield Town A.F.C. seasons}}\n* [[Football League Second Division|Division 2]]: [[1910\u201311 in English football|1910\u201311]] \u2013 [[1919\u201320 in English football|1919\u201320]]\n* [[Football League First Division|Division 1]]: [[1920\u201321 in English football|1920\u201321]] \u2013 [[1951\u201352 in English football|1951\u201352]]\n* [[Football League Second Division|Division 2]]: [[1952\u201353 in English football|1952\u201353]]\n* [[Football League First Division|Division 1]]: [[1953\u201354 in English football|1953\u201354]] \u2013 [[1955\u201356 in English football|1955\u201356]]\n* [[Football League Second Division|Division 2]]: [[1956\u201357 in English football|1956\u201357]] \u2013 [[1969\u201370 in English football|1969\u201370]]\n* [[Football League First Division|Division 1]]: [[1970\u201371 in English football|1970\u201371]] \u2013 [[1971\u201372 in English football|1971\u201372]]\n* [[Football League Second Division|Division 2]]: [[1972\u201373 in English football|1972\u201373]]\n* [[Football League Third Division|Division 3]]: [[1973\u201374 in English football|1973\u201374]] \u2013 [[1974\u201375 in English football|1974\u201375]]\n* [[Football League Fourth Division|Division 4]]: [[1975\u201376 in English football|1975\u201376]] \u2013 [[1979\u201380 in English football|1979\u201380]]\n* [[Football League Third Division|Division 3]]: [[1980\u201381 in English football|1980\u201381]] \u2013 [[1982\u201383 in English football|1982\u201383]]\n* [[Football League Second Division|Division 2]]: [[1983\u201384 in English football|1983\u201384]] \u2013 [[1987\u201388 in English football|1987\u201388]]\n* [[Football League Third Division|Division 3]]: [[1988\u201389 in English football|1988\u201389]] \u2013 [[1991\u201392 in English football|1991\u201392]]\n