1)''': [[2017 EFL Championship play-off Final|2017]]\n\n'''[[List of winners of English Football League One and predecessors|Third Division/League One]] (third tier)'''\n\n* ''Promoted'': [[1982\u201383 in English football|1982\u201383]]\n* '''Play-offs Winners (2)''': [[1995 Football League Second Division play-off Final|1995]], [[2012 Football League One play-off Final|2012]]\n\n'''[[List of winners of English Football League Two and predecessors|Fourth Division/League Two]] (fourth tier)'''\n\n* '''Champions (1)''': [[1979\u201380 in English football|1979\u201380]]\n* '''Play-offs Winners (1)''': [[2004 Football League Third Division play-off Final|2004]]\n\n===Cup===\n'''[[FA Cup]]'''\n*'''Winners (1)''': [[1922 FA Cup Final|1921\u201322]]\n*''Runners-up'': [[1920 FA Cup Final|1919\u201320]], [[1928 FA Cup Final|1927\u201328]], [[1930 FA Cup Final|1929\u201330]], [[1938 FA Cup Final|1937\u201338]]\n\n'''[[Football League Cup]]'''\n*''Semi-finalists'': [[1967\u201368 Football League Cup|1967\u201368]]\n\n'''[[FA Community Shield|FA Charity Shield]]'''\n*'''Winners (1)''': [[1922 FA Charity Shield|1922]]'''\n\n'''[[Football League Trophy]]'''\n*''Runners-up'': [[1994 Football League Trophy Final|1993\u201394]]\n*''Area finalists'': [[2001\u201302 Football League Trophy|2001\u201302]], [[2010\u201311 Football League Trophy|2010\u201311]]\n\n'''[[Yorkshire Electricity Cup]]'''\n*'''Winners (1)''': [[1994\u201395 in English football|1994\u201395]]\n\n===International===\n'''Tournoi de Pentec\u00f4te du Red Star'''\n*'''Winners (1)''': 1921<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rsssf.com/tablesp/paris-tourn.html|title=International Tournaments (Paris) 1904\u20131935|website=www.rsssf.com|access-date=19 August 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180406011838/http://www.rsssf.com/tablesp/paris-tourn.html|archive-date=6 April 2018|url-status=live|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n\n==Personnel==\n\n===Club officials===\n{{fb oi header}}\n{{Fb oi information |bg=  |id=Chairman |i=[[