wner = <!-- or: | owners = -->\n| members = \n| members_year = <!-- Year of members data (if known) -->\n| num_employees = \n| num_employees_year = <!-- Year of num_employees data (if known) -->\n| parent = [[GMM Grammy]] <br /> Hub Ho Hin Bangkok <br /> [[GMM Tai Hub]] (former) <br /> [[GDH 559]]\n| divisions = \n| subsid = \n| module = <!-- Used to embed other templates -->\n| ratio = <!-- Basel III ratio; used for banks only -->\n| rating = <!-- Credit rating; used for banks only -->\n| website = <!-- {{URL|example.com}} -->\n| footnotes = \n}}\n\n'''Nadao Bangkok''' ([[Thai language|Thai]]: \u0e19\u0e32\u0e14\u0e32\u0e27\u0e1a\u0e32\u0e07\u0e01\u0e2d\u0e01), or the registered name of the company, Nadao Bangkok Co., Ltd. is a television production company, [[film studio]], and [[artist management]]. The studio is currently an subsidiary of [[GDH 559]], and is established by [[Songyos Sugmakanan]] on September 9, 2009. The actors under the company are teen actors, and as of 2016, there are nearly 40 actors.<ref>[https://www.matichonweekly.com/in-depth/article_3168 \u0e1f\u0e31\u0e07 \u0e22\u0e49\u0e07 \u0e17\u0e23\u0e07\u0e22\u0e28 \u0e27\u0e34\u0e1e\u0e32\u0e01\u0e29\u0e4c \u201c\u0e21\u0e32\u0e23\u0e4c\u0e0a \u0e15\u0e48\u0e2d \u0e41\u0e1a\u0e07\u0e04\u0e4c \u0e2a\u0e01\u0e32\u0e22\u201d]</ref>\n\nIts most well-known work is [[Hormones: The Series]].\n\n==Actors==\n===Current===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=16em|\n'''Senior'''\n* [[Sunny Suwanmethanont]] (Sunny)\n* [[Chantavit Dhanasevi]] (Ter)\n* Suvikrom Amaranon (Per)\n* Ratchu Surajaras (Vaan)\n\n'''First Gen'''\n* Sirachuch Chienthaworn (Michael)\n* [[Gunn Junhavat]] (Gunn)\n* [[Thanapob Leeratanakajorn]] (Tor)\n* Napat Chokejindachai (Top)\n* Oabnithi Wiwattanawarang (Oab)\n* Awat Ratanapintha (Ud)\n* Sedthawut Anusit (Tou)\n* Tonhon Tantivejakul (Ton)\n* [[Sananthachat Thanapatpisal]] (Fon)\n* [[Kemisara Paladesh]] (Belle)\n\n'''Next Gen'''\n* Kritsanapoom Pibulsonggram (JJ)\n* [[Thiti Mahayotaruk]] (Bank)\n*