 We Trust]]\n| Nappon Gomarachun<br />[[Patravadi Mejudhon]]<br />[[Songsit Roongnophakunsri]]<br />Saksit Tangthong<br />[[Kathaleeya McIntosh]]<br />Sopitnapa Choompanee<br />[[Apasiri Nitibhon]]<br />Phollawat Manuprasert<br />Supoj Chancharoen<br />Kejmanee Wattanasin<br />Pimmara Charoenpakdee<br />[[Thanapob Leeratanakajorn]]<br />Kritsanapoom Pibulsonggram<br />[[Teeradon Supapunpinyo]]<br />[[Chonlathorn Kongyingyong]]<br />[[Lapat Ngamchaweng]]<br />Paris Intarakomalyasut<br />Sivakorn Adulsuttikul<br />Jackrin Kungwankiatichai<br />Vachirawich Aranthanawong<br />[[Kanyawee Songmuang]]<br />Sawanya Paisarnpayak<br />Pitisak Yaowananon<br />Chavalit Chittanant<br />[[Thaneth Warakulnukroh]]\n| [[Songyos Sugmakanan]]\n| September 14 \u2013 November 10, 2018\n| [[GMM Grammy|One31]]\n| The One Enterprise<br>4NOLOGUE\n|-\n| rowspan = \"2\" | 2019 ||[[Great Men Academy]]|| Chanyapuk Numprasop<br />[[Teeradon Supapunpinyo]]<br />Kritsanapoom Pibulsonggram<br />Paris Intarakomalyasut || Wanweaw Hongvivat<br />Weawawan Hongvivat || February 6 \u2013 March 27, 2019<br> July 5 \u2013 August 30, 2019|| LINE TV<br>[[GMM Grammy|One31]] || LINE Thailand\n|-\n| [[My Ambulance]] || [[Sunny Suwanmethanont]]<br />[[Davika Hoorne]]<br />[[Kanyawee Songmuang]]<br />[[Wongravee Nateetorn]] || Naruebet Kuno || September 6 \u2013 October 26, 2019 || rowspan=\"1\" |[[GMM Grammy|One31]] || The One Enterprise\n|-\n| rowspan = \"2\" | 2020\n| Bad Genius: The Series || Jinjett Wattanasin<br />Plearnpichaya Komalarajun<br />Sawanya Paisarnpayak<br />Paris Intarakomalyasut || Pat Boonitipat || {{N/A|TBA}} || rowspan=\"1\" |[[GMM Grammy|One31]] || [[GDH 559]]\n|-\n| BKPP The Series || Putthipong Assaratanakul<br />Krit Amnuaydechkorn || Naruebet Kuno || July 2020 || rowspan=\"1\" | LINE TV || {{N/A|TBA}}\n|}\n\n===Film===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\" border=\"1\" \n! Year !! Title !! Cast(s) !! Director(s) !! Release date !! Production company\n|-\n|