ry Sunday at 11:00&nbsp;am on [[GMM 25]] / 13:00&nbsp;pm on LINE TV from April 24 to December 25, 2016.\n* Game of Teens \u2013 every Sunday at 11:00&nbsp;am on [[GMM 25]] / 13:00&nbsp;pm on LINE TV from February 5, 2017 to February 18, 2018.\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n[[Category:GDH 559]]\n[[Category:GMM Grammy]]\n[[Category:Film production companies of Thailand]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use mdy dates|date=February 2020}}\n{{Infobox company\n| name = Nadao Bangkok Co., Ltd.\n| logo = \n| logo_size = \n| logo_alt = \n| logo_caption = \n| image = \n| image_size = \n| image_alt = \n| image_caption = \n| trade_name = \n| native_name = \u0e19\u0e32\u0e14\u0e32\u0e27\u0e1a\u0e32\u0e07\u0e01\u0e2d\u0e01\n| native_name_lang = <!-- Use ISO 639-1 code, e.g. \"fr\" for French. For multiple names in different languages, use {{Lang|[code]|[name]}}. -->\n| romanized_name = \n| former_name = \n| type = Limited\n| traded_as = \n| ISIN = \n| ISIN2 = \n| industry = Television production <br /> [[film studio]] <br /> [[talent manager]]\n| genre = \n| fate = \n| predecessor = <!-- or: | predecessors = -->\n| successor = <!-- or: | successors = -->\n| founded = {{Start date and age|2009|09|09}} in [[Bangkok]], Thailand\n| founder = [[Songyos Sugmakanan]]\n| defunct = <!-- {{End date|YYYY|MM|DD}} -->\n| hq_location = 92/14 [[Sukhumvit Road]] 31, Khlong Tan Nuea, [[Watthana District]]<ref>https://smelink.net/company/nadao-bangkok-co-ltd.html</ref>\n| hq_location_city = [[Bangkok]]\n| hq_location_country = [[Thailand]]\n| num_locations = \n| num_locations_year = <!-- Year of num_locations data (if known) -->\n| area_served = <!-- or: | areas_served = -->\n| key_people = [[Songyos Sugmakanan]] <br /> Kriangkrai Vachiratamporn\n| products = Media, film, television, mass media\n| brands = \n| production = \n| production_year = <!-- Year of production data (if known) -->\n| services = \n| revenue = \n| revenue_year = <!-- Year of revenue data (if known) -->\n| operating_income = \n| income_